{
  "stem": "15768.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And my mother and we children waited until my mother could stand it no longer and went to the meeting place where she was absolutely certain my father had been dealt with in an unkind of way.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we went to this old, old storage area near the harbor, which was dark and smelly and horrible.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And there was my father.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And his contact had just left.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And the transaction was that my father paid him probably out of some of the jewelry that he had tucked away and this man drove an ambulance from Lille to Paris, which was a fairly good distance.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And for a price, he would take us under the cover, a compartment that was closed over, he would take us in this compartment in ambulance and deposit us in Paris.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And so we did, again, with a little bit of nourishment-- not much, because you couldn't get any.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Everything was rationed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We set out on this journey.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And indeed, with some uncomfortable interruptions, he brought us to Paris.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Once we were in Paris, my father found out there was no one there that he, that he knew of the family.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And so we stopped somewheres in an outdoor cafe, which looked a little tempting for a cup of coffee or so.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Coffee wasn't what coffee is now.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And while we were sitting there, at adjoining table, there were two women, obviously refugees, speaking with a heavy German accent, a Viennese accent.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And at some point, my father brought up the courage to address them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And the one woman said, yes, we-- my husband is very active in helping refugees.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And he'll be, he'll be here in about five minutes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And then he will assist you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And this was our next guardian angel.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
